<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-us">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>URL Shortener</title>
    <meta name="description"
          content="ShortURL is a url shortener to reduce a long link. Use our tool to shorten links and then share them, in addition you can monitor traffic statistics.">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="icons/http.png">
    <meta property="og:title" content="ShortenURL - URL Shortener">
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div id="logo">
        <a href="#" class="logo">Shorten URL</a>
    </div>
</header>
<main>
    <% if(!error){ %>
        <section id="urlbox">
            <h1>Paste the URL to be shortened</h1>
            <form method="post" id="form">
                <div class="formurl">
                    <label>
                        <input id="originalUrl" type="text" name="originalUrl" oninput="disableResultView()" required>
                    </label>
                    <div class="formbutton">
                        <input type="submit" value="Shorten URL">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
            <p class="boxtextcenter">A free tool to shorten a URL or reduce a link<br>Use our URL Shortener to create a
                shortened link making it easy to remember</p>
        </section>
    <% } %>
    <% if (result) { %>
        <div id="result">
            <section id="resultbox">
                <br><br>
                <div class="formurl" style="max-width: 400px;">
                    <label for="shortenurl"></label><input id="shortenurl" type="text" value="<%= result %>" onClick="">
                    <div class="formbutton">
                        <input type="button" data-clipboard-target="#shortenurl" class="copy" value="Copy URL"
                               onclick="copyToClipboard()">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="formurl" style="max-width: 70%; display: block;">
                    <div id="balloon" style="display: none">URL Copied</div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (error) { %>
    <section id="content">
        <h1>An error occurred!</h1>
        <p>The <b>URL is not valid</b>, make sure the URL you tried to shorten is correct.</p>
        <p>Possible errors:</p>
        <ul>
            <li class="list">Check if the domain is correct</li>
            <li class="list">Check if the site is online</li>
            <li class="list">Check the length of the url is not too small</li>
            <li class="list">Check the address bars and punctuation</li>
            <li class="list">The URL may have been blocked</li>
            <li class="list">The url may have been reported</li>
            <li class="list">Make sure the url does not contain spam</li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href="<%= config.homeUrl %>" class="colorbutton">
                <img src="./icons/icon-back.png" alt="back icon" style="height: 30px; width: 30px"> Go Back</a></p>
    </section>
    <% } %>
</main>
<footer>
    <div id="footerbox">
        <div>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear().toString() %> ShortenUrl - Tool to shorten a long link.</div>
    </div>
</footer>
<script type="text/javascript" src="script.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>